question: Na-xie hong-fa/lun-bun sī iōng-chhiú-ko kó͘-sin khah sin-ê/ko-kip ê LLM model lâi chòe?

Tī chit-ê lia̍t-chhut ê hong-hoat/lun-bûn tang-tiong, ū kúi-ê bûn-chiat-tek lia̍t-chhut sái-iōng GPT sè-liân (chham-khó GPT-4, GPT3.5, GPT-4-Turbo, he̍k-chiá kóng-lâng-lâng-tang GPT sè-liân ê ki-khiaⁿ bôa-hêng)?
Hia khi-tsu, teh hōo 'investment' chòe-chòe it ê èng-iōng ê sî, ū ēng tio̍h siánn-sòe ê dataset?
Kāi-ti-kàu GPT3.5 kàu GPT-4 ê GPT bô-hêng ê chin-hóa, khòaⁿ chiàⁿ toh ê piáu-ta̍t, chē-chē ê èng-iōng ia̍h-sī chu-liāu tùi tû khó-í khòaⁿ-tiāⁿ ê sî-bīn sī sím-mih tui-tui-ê piàn-hòa?
answer: Ūi GPT3.5 ê hong-hoat (GPT-InvestAR) sī tiàm 'kó͘-chha̍h tâu-chu' iōng Kōda S&P 500 ê chu-liāu. Iōng koh khah chìn-pō͘ ê GPT-4 (MarketSenseAI kap Ploutos) ê hong-hoat sī tiàm koh khah cheng-tô chē ê èng-iōng, chhin-chhiūⁿ 'kó͘-chha̍h soán-tó kap tâu-chu ê lí-lāi' kap 'kó͘-chha̍h ūn-tōng', iōng S&P 100 kap ha̍k-su̍t lūn-bûn ê chu-liāu. Chit-ê tui-tui ê hong-hoat sī kóng koh khah chìn-pō͘ ê bô-hêng ē-sái kiám-chhài koh khah chheng-tō chē ê èng-iōng.

Tùi chit ê piáu, LLM model ê sù-siat-sèng kap in sū-iōng ê su-liāu lūi-hêng chi kan ū siáⁿ-mih bīn-chá-bīn ê koan-hē a?

Ūi-tiâu-chiah, khah kóng-tōa-khuán kái-sò͘ ê 'GPT-based models' kap khah khoah-bīn, bô te̍k-tēng chòe-iâⁿ ê su-liāu, chhin-chhiūⁿ Common Crawl kap Wikipedia tâng-chái. Chit ê sī chí-bîng kóng-tōa-khuán ê model ē iōng tī khah khoah-bīn ê hun-sek, chi̍t-pâng chi̍t-pâng ê, chin chìn-pò ê model ē si̍t-chè tī khah te̍k-tēng ê châi-bū jīm-bū.
